ComicInfo.Title: Memphis & Beyond the Infinite
ComicInfo.Series: Grumble Memphis and Beyond The Infinite!
ComicInfo.Summary: Brand new jumping on point! Eddie, the small-time crook stuck in a pug's body, and Tala, Eddie's estranged (and part-demon) daughter, are going on their most bizarre, action-packed, and emotional adventure yet! Across the stars, and beyond the edges of reality, Tala's mother is held captive by the evil S'Taera. Joined on the rescue mission by Tala's ex-pro-wrester uncles and their armed militia of inter-dimensional mutants, Eddie and Tala will need to atone for the sins of their pasts and start working together (for once) or they may find themselves lost... beyond the infinite!
